#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# NotesInstallFromServer
#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Set up the server/computer you will do the installation on to boot from the net-
work using PXE/DHCP.

If you set up PXE correctly you should be in the Redhat Linux Install program.

Follow the installation as directed/desired.

#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Disk Druid Note.
#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Do not partition sdb or anaconda will crash.

